entity.name: Updates on the Covid-19 situation in the Philippines
entity.description: This page provides real-time updates on the Covid-19 situation from trusted and official sources.

text: BREAKING: The Philippines has reached the 80k mark in COVID-19 cases with 80,448 confirmed cases, after the DOH reported 2,110 new confirmed cases on Sunday, July 26. Recoveries now at 26,110 with 389 new recoveries, while deaths now at 1,932, with 39 new deaths. https://t.co/qyO6KI8xYY
